    <!-- About -->
    <string name="about">About</string>
    <string name="about_version">Version %1$s</string>
    <string name="about_description">ApexMark is a lightweight, fully local clipboard converter: one tap from the bubble or notification switches Markdown, WPS clipboard, and HTML for pasting into WeChat, WPS, Feishu, browsers, and more. No background clipboard monitoring, no network. v1.1.0 streamlines notifications and keeps default tables neutral. WPS- and HTML-oriented writes put rendered body text in the plain-text slot so paste-as-text stays free of Markdown syntax noise; three or more consecutive newlines collapse to one paragraph break (one blank line). Informal or messy sources may not preserve full rich layout—readable plain text is still kept when a faithful conversion is not possible.</string>
